"{\n    \"explanation\": \"The paper focuses on the use of digital diabetes management technologies (DDMTs) like CGM, mobile apps, and telemedicine, which directly relates to continuous glucose monitoring (CGM) data and the application of technology in diabetes management. It does not primarily involve electronic health records, medical imaging, genomic data, or clinical notes processed via NLP.\",\n    \"class_labels\": [\"continuous_glucose_monitoring_(cgm)_data\"]\n}"